  <label class="quiz-option"><input type="radio" name="quiz-09-a" value="1"> Sequence diagram — it shows the order of interactions</label>
  <label class="quiz-option"><input type="radio" name="quiz-09-a" value="2"> Use case diagram — it shows user goals without implementation detail</label>
  <label class="quiz-option"><input type="radio" name="quiz-09-a" value="3"> Activity diagram — it shows every step of each process</label>
